Quovo is an investment management platform that reimagines the world’s most powerful portfolio tools as an easy‐to‐use cloud application. Quovo aggregates financial information empowering investors to better understand and manage their portfolios. Quovo leverages patent‐pending technology to drive down IT costs and integrate functions traditionally segregated by existing service providers. Quovo applies the latest best practices for product design and user experience in order to adapt high‐end data analytics into an intuitive, seamless product.
